@startuml Current Architecture - gocaving.ai (Phase 1)
!define RECTANGLE class

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam backgroundColor #F0F0F0
skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor<<frontend>> #10b981
  BackgroundColor<<service>> #3b82f6
  BackgroundColor<<data>> #f59e0b
  BorderColor #1e293b
}

title gocaving.ai - Current Architecture (Static Site + Netlify Forms)

package "User Browser" {
  [Web Browser] <<frontend>>
}

package "GitHub" {
  [Repository\ngo-caving-ai] <<data>>
}

package "Netlify CDN" {
  [Static Site\nHTML/CSS/JS] <<frontend>>
  [Netlify Forms] <<service>>
  [Form Storage] <<data>>
  [SSL/HTTPS] <<service>>
}

package "GoDaddy DNS" {
  [DNS Records\ngocaving.ai] <<service>>
}

package "External Resources" {
  [Tailwind CDN] <<service>>
  [Cave Images\n(assets/)] <<data>>
}

' Relationships
[Web Browser] --> [DNS Records\ngocaving.ai] : 1. Resolve domain
[DNS Records\ngocaving.ai] --> [Static Site\nHTML/CSS/JS] : 2. Points to Netlify
[Web Browser] --> [Static Site\nHTML/CSS/JS] : 3. HTTPS request
[Static Site\nHTML/CSS/JS] --> [Tailwind CDN] : Load CSS
[Static Site\nHTML/CSS/JS] --> [Cave Images\n(assets/)] : Load images
[Web Browser] --> [Netlify Forms] : 4. Submit form data
[Netlify Forms] --> [Form Storage] : 5. Store submissions
[Repository\ngo-caving-ai] --> [Static Site\nHTML/CSS/JS] : Auto-deploy on push

note right of [Netlify Forms]
  Two forms:
  - email-updates
  - ai-caving-feedback

  Features:
  - Spam filtering (honeypot)
  - CSV export
  - Email notifications
end note

note right of [Static Site\nHTML/CSS/JS]
  Content:
  - Hero with background
  - Upcoming discussions
  - Projects & Tools
  - Past recordings
  - Feedback form
end note

note left of [Repository\ngo-caving-ai]
  GitHub Actions:
  - Push to main
  - Triggers Netlify build
  - Auto-deploy (30-60s)
end note

@enduml
